OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784909938
OL,3,C'First-of-its-kind' police report
OL,4,Creveals rise in sexual offences
OL,6,FCrime recorded in Jersey has remained
OL,7,Fstable in recent years, but the number
OL,8,Fof sexual offences has increased,
OL,9,Faccording to a first-of-its-kind
OL,10,Fpolicing report.
OL,12,FStates of Jersey Police's new Crime
OL,13,Fand Policing Statistics breaks down
OL,14,Ftotal criminal offences and police
OL,15,Fconduct allegations for the first time.
OL,17,FThe force hopes the new publication
OL,18,Fwill improve transparency and
OL,19,Faccountability, and reaffirm their
OL,20,Fcommitment to public understanding of
OL,21,Fwhat they do.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
