OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784909938
OL,3,C'First-of-its-kind' police report
OL,4,Creveals rise in sexual offences
OL,6,F'Recorded Crime' refers to criminal
OL,7,Foffences that have been formally
OL,8,Flogged by the police following a
OL,9,Freport or detection.
OL,11,FPolice say that quarterly figures have
OL,12,Fremained stable since 2022.
OL,14,FOverall crime levels peaked in 2024
OL,15,Fwith 3,484 recorded crimes.
OL,17,FSexual offences have increased year-on-
OL,18,Fyear since 2022, increasing by around
OL,19,F50% between then and 2025.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784909938
OL,3,C'First-of-its-kind' police report
OL,4,Creveals rise in sexual offences
OL,6,FOffences against the Person - which
OL,7,Fincludes assaults, abusive
OL,8,Fcommunication, and domestic abuse
OL,9,Foffences - saw a spike in the second
OL,10,Fquarter of 2026 with 172 offences in
OL,11,FMay alone.
OL,13,FDrug offences, however, have seen a
OL,14,Fsteady decline over the past four
OL,15,Fyears - down from 170 in 2022 to 115
OL,16,Flast year, although no statistics were
OL,17,Fgiven for 2026.
OL,19,FDriving offences also dropped from a
OL,20,Frecord number in 2024, with arrests
OL,21,Fand stop and searches also down.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
