OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784909938
OL,3,C'First-of-its-kind' police report
OL,4,Creveals rise in sexual offences
OL,6,FThe report also reveals an increase in
OL,7,FPolice Conduct complaints - with 88
OL,8,Fcomplaints last year.
OL,10,FTotal police complaints by year:
OL,12,FMost complaints were relating to
OL,13,F'Performance of Duties', followed by
OL,14,F'Use of Force & Abuse of Authority'.
OL,16,FThe breakdown of Police Conduct
OL,17,Ffigures hopes to replicate the
OL,18,Fmethodology of Jersey Police Complaint
OL,19,FAuthority reporting.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784909938
OL,3,C'First-of-its-kind' police report
OL,4,Creveals rise in sexual offences
OL,6,FThe report will now be published twice
OL,7,Fa year, but police warn that crime
OL,8,Ffigures alone do not capture all they
OL,9,Fdo to keep islanders safe.
OL,11,F"The publication forms part of the
OL,12,Forganisation's commitment to
OL,13,Ftransparency, accountability and
OL,14,Finforming public understanding of
OL,15,Fpolicing on the Island," the States of
OL,16,FJersey Police have stated on their
OL,17,Fwebsite.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784909938
OL,3,C'First-of-its-kind' police report
OL,4,Creveals rise in sexual offences
OL,6,F"While the report shows recorded crime
OL,7,Fhas reduced from the peak levels seen
OL,8,Fin 2024, States of Jersey Police is
OL,9,Fkeen to emphasise that recorded crime
OL,10,Fis only one measure of policing
OL,11,Factivity.
OL,13,F"Many of the issues placing the
OL,14,Fgreatest demand on policing resources,
OL,15,Fincluding safeguarding vulnerable
OL,16,Fpeople, missing person enquiries,
OL,17,Fpublic protection work and concern for
OL,18,Fwelfare incidents, are not fully
OL,19,Fcaptured within recorded crime
OL,20,Fstatistics."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
